refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
intshmop_write Shmopshmop stringdata intoffset
shmop_write écrit une chaîne dans un bloc de mémoire partagée.

&reftitle.errors;


 If offset is out of range, or a read-only shared memory segment
 should be written to, a ValueError is thrown.

